oldest. I was - I was born and then there were four brothers. And then there were two sisters. And then there were two brothers. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Do you know how old the two were when they died?
