\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Do you know what they died of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 I have no idea because - it was before I was born.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 So you're the eldest then you had four brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Then you had two sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 And two more brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Yes.
