d then there was a brother one and a half years older than me, and then my other brother would be two years - it was more or less two yearly. More or less, yes. It may have been a month or two either way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 How old was your father when you were born or his date of birth if you know that?
