\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 , and you started I suppose - as far as I could think - wheeling coal to feed the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 furnace}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
