Well yes, there was a depression when the - when he was out of work from the forge, there was a depression, and he was more or less working - he would cal it - relief work really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 What was he doing with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 Well - there was a dene - do you remember the dene - do you know the dene - Brinkburn Dene. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Well that was made on - people that were out of work and they gave them - they gave them jobs doing that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 What year would this be, any idea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
Oh - it would be after the - after the first world - oh that would be - that would be after you see. Yes, yes, and that was - yes, and - and then he did go back to the forge but not on - as a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 furnace man}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 , that was a very hard job, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 furnace man}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
. Very hard and hot work. And after - the war he wasn't able to do that work and he just went back doing labouring work, you know - lighter work than that. And - then he - from being about fifty or even less he didn't work at all because - 
the work that he had affected his chest, you see, he worked among coal and - he affected his chest and he - very often had bronchitis and suchlike so he just didn't work.
