\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Oh he was many times out of work. In his kind of work - if the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 forge man
}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  was off - the whole hammer was off. And - his particular }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 forge man}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  - drank very heavily and if he went onto - on the booze then of course the whole - hammer was off and - and maybe for a day or two - maybe for a week on an end or even if - I remember - that job depen
ded coal, so that if there was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15554908\charrsid13503492 any}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
 - coal stoppages or - strikes, which about - round about that time there was a lot of unrest in the coal - fields, then - or if the weather was bad and the coal couldn't be moved very well for the frost or snow in the win
tertime, he was very often off for a week or two. And there was no - no pay in those days, if they were off they were off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 You don't know what date he'd be in the Brinkburn Dene do you?
