 - cricket as we used to play with a piece of wood and suchlike and - oh lots of things that they don't do now. I used to swing round the lamp-}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6503756\charrsid13503492 posts}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
