 you had everything black. They used to wear black for a year and in those days and then they used to go into what they call - half - half mourning. Well they u
sed to wear either mauve or grey things, yes. And they never used to go to any - places of entertainment for nearly a year, if it was - especially if it was a husband, they used to think that was awful if they went to a - a place of - a theatre or a place
 of entertainment within about a year. That was a recognised thing. And if anyone died they always used to - collect round the street for a - for a wreath, and artificial thing in a glass }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6503756\charrsid13503492 
