\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 And - they used to aim at getting you to sign a pledge in those days, that you never would touch strong drink. And lots of us did and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Have you kept to it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 No, not really - I wouldn't say strictly but I am - I am teetotal - I never do drink, except just occasional glass of sherry. }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6503756\charrsid13503492 But I mean 
lots of the children that did sign those things, they would never - I know for a fact they were, they never would keep it up, it was - looking back it was rather young to expect a child to sign something like that. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 And to keep it up for all life. It was too much to expect I'm sure.
