\insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  clubs they were in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Yes, the sick club. A
nd - and then - afterwards - oh before the world war there was a - there was so much a week stopped off the pay at work for a doctor, the works had a doctor. I don't know exactly how much it was but it was very little it was stopped out of their pay, and 
the whole family could - have the doctor. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6503756\charrsid13503492 
And that was a - a Godsend - in our house because - before that when we had to pay for the doctor we'd have to be very - either come out in a rash when my mother would know that it - a doctor would have to be got, b
ut for little ailments they would never dream about getting a doctor, 'cos the simple reason that they couldn't afford to pay doctors bills. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
