\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Oh usual, we used to fight sometimes and - argue and - oh - you - you did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2244570\charrsid13503492 
 didn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  you, I mean, you still do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Was there any one you felt particularly close to?
