\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Why was that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Well there were only a year and a half between us and we were the oldest and we got the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2244570\charrsid13503492 brunt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  edge of all the - other family, we had to deny ourselves more than any of the others because - we were the first born and - we had to look }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2244570\charrsid13503492 after}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  all the others you see. And - so we - sort of shared one another's burdens I would say, my brother and I.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 As a child who did you play with, did you play with your brothers and sisters?
