Or there was a park quite close, North Lodge Park. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 And we used to go there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Did you ever play in other homes?
