d - itchy bay. Itchy bay and guessing games, there used to be lots of little shops round about and you used to see things in the window and - guess and run backwards and forwards. Marbles, skipping ropes, bowlers in those days. An iron bowler we had - and
 it had a hook and you used to run round with it and guide it round with - or a - or a wooden hoop we used to have. Used to be all sorts of games.
