\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Rather like }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6503756\charrsid13503492 hopscotch}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
