Well - when I left school there was a girls club used to be run by - teachers in the training college, there's a training college for teachers in Darlington in those days, and some of the teachers used to run a - took a - a - rented a big
 house in Woodlands Road. And - they used to run a club for girls and - I used to go there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 What did you do there?
