Well - you wouldn't call them hobbies because they were things that you had to do. There was - well there was no choice, we just had to do them. Your main hobby was getting out }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6503756\charrsid13503492 playing}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  which you got so little of that you - you're really enjoyed that.
