hen I was about eleven, an - an aunt of my mother's had a bicycle and - she got a job where she didn't need it and she gave it to me when I was about eleven. And that was - oh, a great joy to me. Yes, it was. I had it for years, 'til it wouldn't go, and I
 made great use of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Who did you used to go cycling with?
