Well I had a - a friend that I used to go with and I very often used to cycle from Darlington to Stockton on it to see my grandma. Eleven miles, yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Did you take part in any sports?
