Yes. I can remember - I can remember the first - picture - places being built in Darlington. I can remember to going to my first one with this old lady 
that lived next door, she was a great friend of mine - friend to me. I used to go in her company, and we used to go - they called it the Picturedrome and it was in the Gladstone Street. You won't remember it but there was what they call a temperance hall 
there, and they used to - the pictures there and I can remember them because - they were all very fart and they used to be like a rain coming down of the -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 You were telling me about the pictures all being speckled?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Yes. Yes. And we used to enjoy going there. They - they used to come - periodically. And this old lady used to take me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 You mentioned about an ox being roasted in the town?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Yes, I can remember when - King George V - his coronation, I was at school then, and I can remember - 
remember my father taking me to the market when they - they roasted an ox - and - you could buy a plate of this ox. That was part of the celebrations and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Were your parents able to give you any pocket money?
