\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 When did that stop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Oh during the war it was stopped you see, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Did you take an interest in politics at all?
