Not an active in - interest, I was interested insofar as - an election always was very exciting. I used to go to political meetings. I - I was very interested to hear the - the different aspects of politics. In those days there was Labour, Liberal
 and Conservative and we always used to go to the meetings because they were exciting and - used to be a lot of heckling and - and - I used to go them, because I wasn't - belonged to any particular -
