\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Did you ever feel under any pressure from anyone to vote for a particular party?
