 felt that that wasn't a fair thing and I went. But I used to be home by - used to leave so that I could be home just after nine because - I had to be in at nine. In fact when I was - up to the time I was married I had to be in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid345345\charrsid13503492 at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  half past nine. I wasn't allowed to stay out after that. Unless it was something very special.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Did you make any new friends at this time, any boys or girls?
