\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Well you met them through your friends that knew them and you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid345345\charrsid13503492 
introduced}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492  to them. I was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid345345\charrsid13503492 introduced}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
 to my husband through a friend. And - in those}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid345345\charrsid13503492  days}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
 young people used to parade about in the main street more than they do now. And down Southend Avenue there was - you know - thee was hole - 
young people used to parade about in those days and - they would stop and talk to boys and - your friend knew one of them and then you would get to know the other, and that's how you - yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9001745 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 Did you ever bring friends home, were you allowed to bring your friends home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8342232 EE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
No. No. No, because there was always - we were always overcrowded in our house really. And I really - my aim - rather was to get away from home when I was older you see, I wanted to get away - I - I spent so much time at home. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid345345\charrsid13503492 Well, well there was no room for - to be yourself really because you had no privacy at all. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14499774\charrsid13503492 
But - to me it was a treat to get outside of home because - you had no privacy to - at home at all with a big family and a small house. So that it was rather a - a release for me to get away or outside of home.
